description:
This beautiful piano instrumental version of the popular song "Whiter Than Snow" is perfect for any occasion! Whether you're planning a winter party or just want to add some festive cheer to your day, this piano instrumental version is the perfect choice!
If you're looking for a karaoke song that will really make your guests feel the holiday spirit, look no further than "Whiter Than Snow!" This uplifting and beautiful song is perfect for any celebration!

First Line: Dear Jesus, I long to be perfectly whole
Title: Whiter than Snow
Author: James Nicholson (1872)
Music performed by Mr. C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters' Karaoke youtube channel.
